### Del statement
---
!!!<p><span class="yellow-status">In progress</span></p>
---
*Delete values.
*Delete arrays, and other builtin data structures without deleting content.
---
```yaksha
def main() -> int:
    a: Array[int]
    defer del a
    arrput(a, 1)
    arrput(a, 2)
    arrput(a, 3)
    println(a[0])
    return 0
```
;Compiles to `free` or other runtime functions.
